name: Grape Marmalade
description: Grape Marmalade is an indica-dominant hybrid marijuana strain made from an unknown cross of Grape Pie. This strain produces a relaxing body high that is enjoyable but not overwhelming. Some consumers have reported feeling a tingling sensation when smoking Grape Marmalade. This strain features a tasty flavor profile that has been described as fruity. Medical marijuana patients choose Grape Marmalade to help relieve symptoms associated with stress and pain.
